e potential association of viral diversity with the host's diet. These findings provide significant insight into viral bat diversity in French Guiana belonging to the Amazonian biome and emphasize that habitats and the host's dietary ecology may drive the viral diversity in the bat communities investigated.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Salmier, Arielle", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tirera, Sourakhata", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "De Thoisy, Benoit", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Franc, Alain", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Darcissac, Edith", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Donato, Damien", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bouchier, Christiane", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lacoste, Vincent", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lavergne, Anne", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Forrester, Naomi", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/0a75ecdc4146f85ea596856be504d681", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/48b89faaae09ea15892277bac09e8b69174861b9b7ae5f2a21f50dcf5fd7f162", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/EF3BPQVN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/EF3BPQVN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/23d725938c4bc0a5fd5f466a0bcbc2d4!/b115649-118117", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type